{"root":{"data":{"id":"di5b7esnleg0","created":1777432414619,"text":"案例","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di5b7k8u72o0","created":1777432426482,"text":"需求分析","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di5fg1pu0d40","created":1777444375868,"text":"把需求获取阶段得到的零散需求进行整合，并对冲突\n进行沟通协调，把内容和相关干系人达成共识","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di5fiz7vc2o0","created":1777444605520,"text":"1. 建立需求分析模型\n2. 创建用户界面原型\n3. 分析需求可行性\n4. 确定需求优先级\n5. 创建数据字典\n6. 使用QFD（Quality Function Deployment）","layout_right_offset":{"x":17,"y":57},"font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"di5idyex97s0","created":1777452675279,"text":"架构设计","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di5iekmqbzc0","created":1777452723640,"text":"质量属性","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di5if0vkego0","created":1777452759003,"text":"质量属性效用树","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di5ife4xkfs0","created":1777452787867,"text":"质量属性判定","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"di5iem3jiww0","created":1777452726833,"text":"架构风格","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di5in8vylww0","created":1777453403354,"text":"定义：","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di5j6rroco00","created":1777454933373,"text":"MVC：\n控制器：处理用户交互，负\n责从视图读取数据，控制用\n户输入，冰向模型发送数据\n模型：处理业务逻辑\n视图：处理用户显示","layout_left_offset":{"x":-103,"y":6},"font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"di5ien9u6zs0","created":1777452729391,"text":"典型架构","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di5ietqqwrk0","created":1777452743474,"text":"架构评估","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di659gvxtlc0","created":1777517209197,"text":"架构风险"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di659jkje800","created":1777517215038,"text":"在架构设计决策中，可能导致系统出现问题（如性能批瓶颈、单点故障、机密泄露等）的潜在隐患"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"di65chjb90w0","created":1777517445703,"text":"敏感点"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di65ck15cmw0","created":1777517451135,"text":"在架构设计中，一个或多个构件的特性，这个特性的变化会对系统的某个质量属性产生影响"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"di65d43rak00","created":1777517494828,"text":"权衡点"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di65dbswxaw0","created":1777517511587,"text":"在架构设计中，一个或多个构件的特定属性的变化会对系统的多个质量属性产生显著影响"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"di6aa38l4co0","created":1777531363400,"text":"数据仓库"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di6aa4k9phs0","created":1777531366284,"text":"特点"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di6aa6j1xnk0","created":1777531370564,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}